            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C.) In nomine sanctae et individuae trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/239">Otto</persName> divina ordinante
                        clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Noscat omnium
                        sanctae dei aecclesiae ac nostrorum fidelium presentium scilicet et
                        futurorum industria, quod <persName key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/652">Heinricus <rs key="#Marquis/duke">Karentanorum
                                dux</rs></persName> nostrae humiliter <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >suggessit</rs> magestati, quatinus locum qui nuncupatur Insula que+ est
                        sita in <placeName key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#places/957"
                                ><geogName key="#Other_administrative_unit" ref="#estates/1497"><rs
                                    key="#Other_administrative_unit"
                            >Istria</rs></geogName></placeName>, cu[m] suis pertinentiis et
                        retibitionibus, quam dudum videlicet beate+ memorie+ <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #parentOf" ref="#people/173"><rs key="#parentOf"
                                >genitor noster</rs>
                        </persName>cuidam<persName ref="#people/650"
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Venditio #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention"
                            > Uenetico Uitali Candiano</persName> nominato <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">per precepti paginam</rs> tribuit, nos id
                        ipsum ab eodem Uenetico <rs key="#Venditio">venditum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Patriarchs" ref="#people/651">Rodaldo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Patriarchs">patriarche</rs> suisque successoribus per auctoritatis
                        nostre+ preceptum confirmare dignaremur. Cuius suggestioni libenter assensum
                        prebentes locum qui dicitur<placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Riverbed #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rent_in_kind #Fountains #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity"
                            ref="#places/956">
                            <rs
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Insula</rs></placeName> cum suis <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >apendiciis</rs> tam infra<placeName
                            key="#Cities #Rivers #Riverbed #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rent_in_kind #Fountains #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity"
                            ref="#places/593">
                            <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> Iustinopolim</placeName> quam extra
                        que+ vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Riverbed #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Casalini/fundamenta #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rent_in_kind #Fountains #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity"
                            ref="#places/593">Capras</placeName>, e+que in <rs key="#Mountains"
                            >montibus</rs> ut in planitiis cum omnibus <rs key="#Census"
                            >censibus</rs> et <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">retibitionibus</rs> sive <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">aquis </rs><rs key="#Riverbed #Fountains">aquarumque
                            ductibus fontaneis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta #Cereals">casaliuis clausuris</rs>
                        <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Oil">olivetis</rs> cuctis et incultis <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">ripaticis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, ita integre uti in nostra permansit
                        potesta[te], eidem Rodaldo venerabili patriarche, rectori videlicet <orgName
                            key="#Census #Profits_of_justice #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Immunity #Mother_churches #Patriarchs"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/92"><rs key="#Mother_churches">sanctae
                                Aquilegensis aecclesiae</rs></orgName>, suisque sugcessoribus
                        concedimus atque largimur habendi potestatem, omnium sciliet hominum
                        contradictione remota, eo videlicet ordine quatinus <rs key="#Immunity"
                            >nullus dux marchio episcopus comes vicecomes sculdascius gastaldius
                            [vel] aliquis publice+ rei exactor </rs>nec non magna parvaque nostri
                        imperii persona inquietare aut molestare presumat aut <rs
                            key="#Profits_of_justice">placitum</rs> tenere sive aliquod officium
                        construere nisi predicti patriarche licencia. Insuper etiam pro remedio
                        anime+ nostrae omnem censum quem predicte+ Insule+ homines infra civitatem
                        Iustinopolim in domibus vel ceteris rebus regiae potestati atque imperiali
                        actenus persolvere visi sunt, in predicti Rodaldi patriarche suorumque
                        successorum potestatem firmiter tradidimus ac donavimus. Si quis vero huius
                        nostri precepti violator extiterit aut consentire noluerit, sciat se procul
                        dubio compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">mille libras obtimi auri,</rs>
                        medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere+ nostrae</rs> medietatemque
                        supralibato Rodaldo patriarche+ suisque successoribus quibus molestiam
                        intulerit. Et ut hoc inconvulse servetur in posterum, huius pagine+
                        preceptum manu nostra s[ubter] roborantes sigillo nostro iussimus insigniri.
                        Signum domni Ottonis invictisimi (M.) imperatoris augusti. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Erchempertus">Egbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName><name
                                ref="Wiligis">Uuilligisi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicappellani</rs> recognovi. (SI. D.) Datum XVI.
                        kal. mai. anno dominice+ incarnationis [DCCCCLX]XVI, indictione V, anno vero
                        regni domni Ottonis XVI, imperii X; actum Ingelen[heim; feliciter.] </ab>
                </div>
